snippet.title: Touhou Puppet Dance Performance - Shard of Dreams - Extended - Trailer
snippet.description:
The time has finally come! The Extended mod that adds a lot of new features to Touhou Puppet Dance Performance has finally been released!

Enjoy the enhanced experience with newer characters from the print works and games beyond 15!


Learn more about it & get it from here: http://en.tpdpwiki.net/wiki/Mod:Shard_of_Dreams_-_Extended_-

And here:
http://gensoushinki.com/index.php?lang=en


Join the TPDP Discord! 
https://discord.gg/0zGPQXeHpqbyVYTa



Get the patch here:
http://gensoushinki.com/index.php?lang=en

Video made by Wower.
